//www.businessbroker.ch/Portals/0/Content/Artikel%20Weltwoche%2011_2012_1.PDF\">Der Traum einer eigenen Firma</a></li>\r\n	<li>August 2012, Artikel im Tagesanzeiger: <a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/Portals/0/Content/Bericht%20Tages-Anzeiger%20Business%20Broker%2004_08_2012_1.pdf\">Diese drei verkuppeln Unternehmer</a></li>\r\n	<li>April 2012, Artikel in der Handelszeitung: <a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/LinkClick.aspx?fileticket=oC1lP5ClzVg%3d&amp;tabid=110&amp;language=de-CH\">Hohe Verkaufskunst</a></li>\r\n	<li>März 2012, Artikel im NZZ Equity Magazin: <a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/LinkClick.aspx?fileticket=UHEuxotj0B0%3d&amp;tabid=110&amp;language=de-CH\">Bekanntes oder Ungewohntes kaufen?</a></li>\r\n	<li>Dezember 2011, Artikel in der Zürcher Wirtschaft: <a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/LinkClick.aspx?fileticket=HHakr5uIL%2bk%3d&amp;tabid=61&amp;language=de-CH\">Erst die Arbeit - und dann?</a></li>\r\n	<li>Oktober 2011, Artikel im KMU-Magazin: <a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/LinkClick.aspx?fileticket=WC76BT3JqVo%3d&amp;tabid=61&amp;language=de-CH\">Auf dem Weg zum Unternehmenskauf</a></li>\r\n	<li>August 2011, Bericht Schweiz Aktuell: <a href=\"http://www.videoportal.sf.tv/video?id=9fe7af96-8246-46c4-95a1-5d9ef2c4fed0\">Sendung vom 05.08.2011</a></li>\r\n	<li>Juni 2011, Artikel in der Unternehmerzeitung: <a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/LinkClick.aspx?fileticket=Vggwx0mHdd8%3d&amp;tabid=61&amp;language=de-CH\">Firma zu verkaufen!</a></li>\r\n	<li>Oktober 2010, Artikel im Swiss Equity Magazin: <a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/LinkClick.aspx?fileticket=p%2fy60k9c%2fAA%3d&amp;tabid=61&amp;language=de-CH\">Zu verkaufen: Laden um die Ecke</a></li>\r\n	<li>September 2010, Artikel in Zürcher Wirtschaft: <a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/LinkClick.aspx?fileticket=MgI26ZJT2HE%3d&amp;tabid=61&amp;language=de-CH\">Die Erfolgsfaktoren</a></li>\r\n	<li>August 2010, Artikel im Balance Magazin: <a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/LinkClick.aspx?fileticket=ihbIYC%2fSK3I%3d&amp;tabid=61&amp;language=de-CH\">Ein eigenes Geschäft, Die ultimative Selbstverwirklichung</a></li>\r\n	<li>Dezember 2009, Interview auf dem KMU-Portal Seco: <a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/LinkClick.aspx?fileticket=bvVGUYXFSnU%3d&amp;tabid=61&amp;language=de-CH\">Der Markt muss spielen können</a></li>\r\n	<li>August 2009, Artikel in der Handelszeitung: <a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/LinkClick.aspx?fileticket=lOuVhBhVTfY%3d&amp;tabid=61&amp;language=de-CH\">Die M&amp;A-Pipelines füllen sich</a></li>\r\n	<li>August 2009, Artikel im Interview-Magazin: <a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/LinkClick.aspx?fileticket=Sxmi6%2flLTzo%3d&amp;tabid=61&amp;language=de-CH\">Erfolgsfaktoren</a></li>\r\n	<li>Juli 2009, Artikel im Organisator: <a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/LinkClick.aspx?fileticket=7b6jSDxcSi0%3d&amp;tabid=61&amp;language=de-CH\">Firma verkaufen - aber wie?</a></li>\r\n	<li>Mai 2009, Bericht im Cash-TV: <a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/Portals/0/Content/Videos/CashTVBusinessBrokerMp4.html\">Sendung vom 24.05.2009</a></li>\r\n	<li>März 2009, Artikel im KMU-Magazin: <a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/Portals/0/Content/Die%20acht%20Erfolgsfaktoren%20beim%20Unternehmensverkauf.pdf\">Die acht Erfolgsfaktoren beim Unternehmensverkauf</a></li>\r\n	<li>Januar 2009, Artikel in der Handelszeitung: <a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/Portals/0/Content/Special%20Merger.pdf\">Kleine Firmen gut verkaufen</a></li>\r\n	<li>Dezember 2008, Interview auf change.ch: <a href=\"http://change.ch/aktuell/generation-change/nachfolgeregelung.html\">Nachfolgeregelung</a></li>\r\n	<li>Dezember 2008, Interview im cash: <a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/Portals/0/Content/cash-neu-im-geschaeft-26-11-08.pdf\">Neu im Geschäft</a></li>\r\n	<li>Dezember 2008, Artikel im Bülacher Tagblatt: <a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/LinkClick.aspx?fileticket=AC5eiT0UMYQ%3d&amp;tabid=61&amp;language=de-CH\">Nachfolgeplanung früh einleiten</a></li>\r\n	<li>April 2008, Artikel im KMU Life: <a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/Portals/0/Content/KMU%20Life.pdf\">Kaufen statt Gründen</a></li>\r\n	<li>September 2007, Publireportage auf KMU-Next: <a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/Portals/0/Content/Publireportage_v5.pdf\">Business Broker AG: neu, einfach und erfolgsbasiert</a></li>\r\n</ul>','Download Centre','','publish','closed','closed','','download-centre','','','2015-12-18 16:16:29','2015-12-18 16:16:29','',0,'http://localhost/startupbroker/?page_id=90',11,'page','',0),(91,1,'2015-12-18 14:24:56','2015-12-18 14:24:56','','Download Centre','','inherit','closed','closed','','90-revision-v1','','','2015-12-18 14:24:56','2015-12-18 14:24:56','',90,'http://localhost/startupbroker/2015/12/18/90-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(92,1,'2015-12-18 14:25:25','2015-12-18 14:25:25','','References','','publish','closed','closed','','references','','','2015-12-18 14:25:25','2015-12-18 14:25:25','',0,'http://localhost/startupbroker/?page_id=92',12,'page','',0),(93,1,'2015-12-18 14:25:25','2015-12-18 14:25:25','','References','','inherit','closed','closed','','92-revision-v1','','','2015-12-18 14:25:25','2015-12-18 14:25:25','',92,'http://localhost/startupbroker/2015/12/18/92-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(94,1,'2015-12-18 14:25:49','2015-12-18 14:25:49','','References','','publish','closed','closed','','references','','','2015-12-18 14:25:49','2015-12-18 14:25:49','',92,'http://localhost/startupbroker/?page_id=94',1,'page','',0),(95,1,'2015-12-18 14:25:49','2015-12-18 14:25:49','','References','','inherit','closed','closed','','94-revision-v1','','','2015-12-18 14:25:49','2015-12-18 14:25:49','',94,'http://localhost/startupbroker/2015/12/18/94-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(96,1,'2015-12-18 14:26:12','2015-12-18 14:26:12','','Picture gallery','','publish','closed','closed','','picture-gallery','','','2015-12-18 14:26:12','2015-12-18 14:26:12','',92,'http://localhost/startupbroker/?page_id=96',2,'page','',0),(97,1,'2015-12-18 14:26:12','2015-12-18 14:26:12','','Picture gallery','','inherit','closed','closed','','96-revision-v1','','','2015-12-18 14:26:12','2015-12-18 14:26:12','',96,'http://localhost/startupbroker/2015/12/18/96-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(98,1,'2015-12-18 14:26:46','2015-12-18 14:26:46','[contact-form-7 id=\"140\" title=\"startup broker\"]','Contact','','publish','closed','closed','','contact','','','2015-12-20 07:27:38','2015-12-20 07:27:38','',0,'http://localhost/startupbroker/?page_id=98',13,'page','',0),(99,1,'2015-12-18 14:26:46','2015-12-18 14:26:46','','Contact','','inherit','closed','closed','','98-revision-v1','','','2015-12-18 14:26:46','2015-12-18 14:26:46','',98,'http://localhost/startupbroker/2015/12/18/98-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(100,1,'2015-12-18 14:27:03','2015-12-18 14:27:03','<h1>Legal Details</h1>\r\nBusiness Broker AG\r\nFlorastrasse 44\r\nCH-8008 Zürich\r\n\r\nTel.: <a href=\"tel:+41444201111\">+41 (0)44 – 420 11 11</a>\r\nFax: <a href=\"tel:+41444201112\">+41 (0)44 – 420 11 12</a>\r\n<a href=\"mailto:info@businessbroker.ch\" data-rit-email-id=\"info\">info@businessbroker.ch</a>\r\n\r\nVAT No. Switzerland: CHE-113.594.288 MWST\r\nCommercial Register Number Switzerland: CH-020.3.030.936-7\r\n\r\nManaging Director: Britta Häberling\r\nResponsible for content in accordance with §6 MDStV [German State Treaty on Media Services]: Britta Häberling\r\nContact person: Britta Häberling\r\nTel.: <a href=\"tel:+41444201111\">+41 (0)44 – 420 11 11</a>\r\n<h2>Data Protection Notice</h2>\r\nWe treat your personal data confidentially. Your personal data, which you provided to us within the context of establishing contact, is stored by us and processed within the context of establishing contact. This generally involves your name, your e-mail address, your address and your telephone number or telefax number.\r\n\r\nWe use your data exclusively in order to send you our attractive offers. We only use your data for our own purposes and do NOT disclose your data to third parties. You can cancel the use of your personal data at any time by sending us a written notification or by e-mail. After receiving your cancellation, we will immediately discontinue the further sending of information.\r\n\r\nChanges to our business and legal changes can influence our data protection policy. We will update this accordingly and publish it here.\r\n\r\nWith a ruling dated 12 May 1998 (312 O 85/98), the Hamburg Regional Court decided that anyone inserting a link may also share liability for the content of the linked page.\r\n<h2>Liability Disclaimer</h2>\r\nDespite careful content control, we are not liable for external linked contents. Responsibility for the contents of sites linked from this one remains with the operator of those sites.','Legal notice','','publish','closed','closed','','legal-notice','','','2015-12-18 16:17:32','2015-12-18 16:17:32','',0,'http://localhost/startupbroker/?page_id=100',14,'page','',0),(101,1,'2015-12-18 14:27:03','2015-12-18 14:27:03','','Legal notice','','inherit','closed','closed','','100-revision-v1','','','2015-12-18 14:27:03','2015-12-18 14:27:03','',100,'http://localhost/startupbroker/2015/12/18/100-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(102,1,'2015-12-18 14:46:15','2015-12-18 14:46:15','<h1>Buy1 a company – Sell a company – SME succession planning</h1>\r\n<b class=\"lede\">Business Broker AG is the largest and most successful consulting and brokerage company in the SME sector in Switzerland. More than 300 finalised projects are proof of our experience and expertise. We specialise in the sale of small and medium-sized companies in Europe. Our core competencies are buying companies, selling companies, succession planning and business valuations. We provide active and effective support during the purchase and sale of small and medium-sized companies.</b>\r\n<h2>Sell a company</h2>\r\nWe prepare a marketing concept, revise your business deals and put together an attractive company presentation. A higher sales price is attained through active marketing and a professional approach. Risks are avoided and opportunities are used. Legal and tax aspects are clarified. The controlled sales process ensures anonymity and confidentiality. During contract negotiations, we are at your side and working towards the best deal. The time required for commercial sales and the complexity of the process are often underestimated. Experiments during the company\'s succession cost a lot of time and money.\r\n\r\n<strong>Your success is our goal! Therefore, we charge a success fee.</strong>\r\n\r\n<dl class=\"callToAction\"><dt>Further information</dt><dd><a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/en/services/sell-company\" data-rit-tabid=\"100\">Sell a company</a></dd></dl>\r\n<h2>Buy a company</h2>\r\nWe have a large number of attractive companies in our <a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/en/buy-company/business-listings\" data-rit-tabid=\"74\">portfolio</a>. Under the heading “Buy a company” next to the details of the individual company you will find a wealth of valuable information about the purchase of the company. You can also set up an automatic search free of charge. The business purchase is free of commission for the purchaser — we are commissioned by the seller and this is where we receive our fee.\r\n\r\n<dl class=\"callToAction\"><dt>Further information</dt><dd><a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/en/buy-company/business-listings\" data-rit-tabid=\"74\">Buy a company</a></dd></dl>\r\n<h2>Business Valuation</h2>\r\nWe value a company using five different assessment methods. A thorough evaluation by the Company Business Broker AG is often used to determine the realistic market value in court matters.','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','2-revision-v1','','','2015-12-18 14:46:15','2015-12-18 14:46:15','',2,'http://localhost/startupbroker/2015/12/18/2-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(103,1,'2015-12-18 14:46:27','2015-12-18 14:46:27','<h1>Buy a company – Sell a company – SME succession planning</h1>\r\n<b class=\"lede\">Business Broker AG is the largest and most successful consulting and brokerage company in the SME sector in Switzerland. More than 300 finalised projects are proof of our experience and expertise. We specialise in the sale of small and medium-sized companies in Europe. Our core competencies are buying companies, selling companies, succession planning and business valuations. We provide active and effective support during the purchase and sale of small and medium-sized companies.</b>\r\n<h2>Sell a company</h2>\r\nWe prepare a marketing concept, revise your business deals and put together an attractive company presentation. A higher sales price is attained through active marketing and a professional approach. Risks are avoided and opportunities are used. Legal and tax aspects are clarified. The controlled sales process ensures anonymity and confidentiality. During contract negotiations, we are at your side and working towards the best deal. The time required for commercial sales and the complexity of the process are often underestimated. Experiments during the company\'s succession cost a lot of time and money.\r\n\r\n<strong>Your success is our goal! Therefore, we charge a success fee.</strong>\r\n\r\n<dl class=\"callToAction\"><dt>Further information</dt><dd><a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/en/services/sell-company\" data-rit-tabid=\"100\">Sell a company</a></dd></dl>\r\n<h2>Buy a company</h2>\r\nWe have a large number of attractive companies in our <a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/en/buy-company/business-listings\" data-rit-tabid=\"74\">portfolio</a>. Under the heading “Buy a company” next to the details of the individual company you will find a wealth of valuable information about the purchase of the company. You can also set up an automatic search free of charge. The business purchase is free of commission for the purchaser — we are commissioned by the seller and this is where we receive our fee.\r\n\r\n<dl class=\"callToAction\"><dt>Further information</dt><dd><a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/en/buy-company/business-listings\" data-rit-tabid=\"74\">Buy a company</a></dd></dl>\r\n<h2>Business Valuation</h2>\r\nWe value a company using five different assessment methods. A thorough evaluation by the Company Business Broker AG is often used to determine the realistic market value in court matters.','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','2-revision-v1','','','2015-12-18 14:46:27','2015-12-18 14:46:27','',2,'http://localhost/startupbroker/2015/12/18/2-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(104,1,'2015-12-18 14:47:45','2015-12-18 14:47:45','<h1>Corporate transactions (company purchase/company sale) by Business Broker AG</h1>\r\nBusiness Broker AG offers advisory services in connection with the selling and buying of small and medium-sized companies including other tasks and topics concerning corporate transactions.\r\n\r\nBusiness Broker AG is the largest and most successful consultation and mediation company in the SME sector in Switzerland. Over 300 finalised projects are proof of their experience and expertise.\r\n\r\nCompany transactions are typically characterised by several phases with different tasks. Once the goals are defined, numerous working modules are then needed to create transparency. Reviewing all documents avoids any surprises at the time of the conclusion. The attractive corporate presentation simplifies communication. A large number of potential buyers improves the negotiating position on the way to the optimal conclusion of a contract.\r\n\r\nEvery corporate purchase or sale is unique in its development: Companies are complex and unique organisations. Since the goals of the negotiating parties are different from case to case, the procedure must be fully adapted to the respective situation. Only in this way can the best possible solution be obtained for the client.\r\n\r\nBusiness Broker AG knows about the specific needs of small and medium sized companies. We take over the intensive project management, whereby we carry out individual work processes quickly, on time and with absolute discretion.\r\n\r\n<dl class=\"callToAction\"><dt>Ask for our no-obligation information pack</dt><dd><a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/en/contact\" data-rit-tabid=\"62\">Contact</a></dd></dl>','About us','','inherit','closed','closed','','7-revision-v1','','','2015-12-18 14:47:45','2015-12-18 14:47:45','',7,'http://localhost/startupbroker/2015/12/18/7-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(105,1,'2015-12-18 14:48:48','2015-12-18 14:48:48','<h1>Corporate transactions (company purchase/company sale) by Business Broker AG</h1>\r\nBusiness Broker AG offers advisory services in connection with the selling and buying of small and medium-sized companies including other tasks and topics concerning corporate transactions.\r\n\r\nBusiness Broker AG is the largest and most successful consultation and mediation company in the SME sector in Switzerland. Over 300 finalised projects are proof of their experience and expertise.\r\n\r\nCompany transactions are typically characterised by several phases with different tasks. Once the goals are defined, numerous working modules are then needed to create transparency. Reviewing all documents avoids any surprises at the time of the conclusion. The attractive corporate presentation simplifies communication. A large number of potential buyers improves the negotiating position on the way to the optimal conclusion of a contract.\r\n\r\nEvery corporate purchase or sale is unique in its development: Companies are complex and unique organisations. Since the goals of the negotiating parties are different from case to case, the procedure must be fully adapted to the respective situation. Only in this way can the best possible solution be obtained for the client.\r\n\r\nBusiness Broker AG knows about the specific needs of small and medium sized companies. We take over the intensive project management, whereby we carry out individual work processes quickly, on time and with absolute discretion.\r\n\r\n<dl class=\"callToAction\"><dt>Ask for our no-obligation information pack</dt><dd><a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/en/contact\" data-rit-tabid=\"62\">Contact</a></dd></dl>','Business Broker AG','','inherit','closed','closed','','9-revision-v1','','','2015-12-18 14:48:48','2015-12-18 14:48:48','',9,'http://localhost/startupbroker/2015/12/18/9-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(106,1,'2015-12-18 14:49:33','2015-12-18 14:49:33','<h1>Mission</h1>\r\nBusiness Broker AG has made it its mission to facilitate business succession. In order to achieve this goal, we have created a transparent market which makes it easier for buyers and sellers to find each other and where the sale of the business can be processed in an atmosphere of mutual trust and respect. Based on our expertise, we offer the parties a helping hand and guide them through the challenging process with many pitfalls along the way.\r\n\r\nWith great commitment and dedication, our customers have created significant value: They have set up a company and created many jobs. Customers, suppliers and employees rely on the existence of the company as a going concern. A large part of the assets is tied up in the company and can only be realized by selling the business. We are in the same boat and have the same goals as our customers. Thanks to a large number of potential buyers, we offer our customers the opportunity to select and implement the option which works best for them.\r\n\r\nThe benefit for the economy is enormous. It has helped to save over 1,000 jobs, and our customers have received well over CHF 350 million thanks to successful sale of companies.\r\n\r\nCompanies are works of art, and we are committed to conserving them.','Mission','','inherit','closed','closed','','11-revision-v1','','','2015-12-18 14:49:33','2015-12-18 14:49:33','',11,'http://localhost/startupbroker/2015/12/18/11-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(107,1,'2015-12-18 14:50:25','2015-12-18 14:50:25','<h1>Buying and selling companies successfully</h1>\r\n<h2>Business Broker – Best Practice Guide</h2>\r\n<table class=\"content_text\" border=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/Portals/0/Content/BBBookCover.jpg\" alt=\"Business Broker Buch: Unternehmen erfolgreich kaufen und verkaufen\" border=\"0\" /></td>\r\n<td>Book bound, 238 pages, Language German, 2012\r\nOrell Füssli Verlag\r\n\r\nCHF 59.- including VAT\r\n(+ Shipping costs)\r\n<div class=\"callToAction_button\"><a class=\"callToAction_buttonText\" href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/tabid/62/Default.aspx?ct=book\">Order</a></div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<table class=\"content_text\" border=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">Authors:</td>\r\n<td>Andreas Schubert, Reto Meli, Richard Jauch, Fabian Rudin, Jérôme Andermatt (longstanding employee at Business Broker AG)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">Contents:</td>\r\n<td>Every year 5000 small and medium companies are sold in Switzerland. The book is the first practical introduction to best company selling and buying techniques. The seller is specifically shown how to sell his/her company profitably. The buyer learns how to minimise risks when buying. The book explains all the steps from preparing the sale up to signing the sales contract in detail. The reader receives templates of all the documents and checklists. The book helps to avoid expensive, often disastrous errors. Through this the sale of the own business becomes the crowning achievement of a business person’s career and not, as is so often the case, the start of a legal dispute.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p align=\"left\"></p>','The Book','','inherit','closed','closed','','13-revision-v1','','','2015-12-18 14:50:25','2015-12-18 14:50:25','',13,'http://localhost/startupbroker/2015/12/18/13-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(108,1,'2015-12-18 14:52:01','2015-12-18 14:52:01','<h1>Our Teams</h1>\r\n<dl class=\"callToAction\"><dt>Team</dt> <dd><a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/en/about-us/team-switzerland\" data-rit-tabid=\"149\">Switzerland</a></dd></dl>&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<dl class=\"callToAction\"><dt>Team</dt> <dd><a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/en/about-us/team-germany\" data-rit-tabid=\"150\">Germany</a></dd></dl>','Team','','inherit','closed','closed','','15-revision-v1','','','2015-12-18 14:52:01','2015-12-18 14:52:01','',15,'http://localhost/startupbroker/2015/12/18/15-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(109,1,'2015-12-18 14:52:41','2015-12-18 14:52:41','<h1>Career</h1>\r\nA career with Business Broker AG offers the opportunity to work in an interesting and inspiring environment while taking up lots of responsibility. We want to enjoy working and we want to make progress. We have high demands but your efforts will be rewarded.\r\n\r\nWe work independently and believe that only if we surpass our internal and external client\'s expectations they will be fully satisfied. This is our promise and it should be yours as well.\r\n\r\nIn our working culture, we are success-oriented and, at the same time, we put emphasis on good cooperation. Important factors are a fair and respectful approach and a direct, open and honest communication within the team as well as towards our clients.\r\n\r\nWe have a very flat hierarchy. It is not the position that counts, but the argument and, in the end, the success. If you are looking for responsibility, you will get the opportunity to transform your ideas and visions. Once you have proved that you are successful, we will discuss together what kind of further steps you can take in your career.\r\n\r\nIt is not important to know everything right from the start; however, you must be willing to learn and to make progress. Changes and responsibility offer many chances - do you want to take them?\r\n<h2>Requirements</h2>\r\nAccording to your personal background and to your interests we will offer you several possibilities. Different perspectives are fruitful. Therefore, we are not looking for staff with a specific professional education, but for people with different professional and personal experiences.\r\n\r\nWhat we expect:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Completed higher education</li>\r\n	<li>Several years of successful professional activity</li>\r\n	<li>Interest for economical relations</li>\r\n	<li>Business- as well as client-oriented thinking and acting</li>\r\n	<li>Capacity to work independently and success-oriented</li>\r\n	<li>High degree of self-motivation, in order to be able to cope with difficulties</li>\r\n	<li>Capacity not only to listen carefully, but also to draw the right conclusions and to initiate its carrying out</li>\r\n	<li>Willing to go the extra mile for your clients</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<dl class=\"callToAction\"><dt>Please send your complete application to</dt><dd><a href=\"mailto:karriere@businessbroker.ch\">karriere@businessbroker.ch</a></dd></dl>','Career','','inherit','closed','closed','','18-revision-v1','','','2015-12-18 14:52:41','2015-12-18 14:52:41','',18,'http://localhost/startupbroker/2015/12/18/18-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(110,1,'2015-12-18 14:56:23','2015-12-18 14:56:23','<h1>Our Locations</h1>\r\n<article>\r\n<h2>Switzerland</h2>\r\n<div><dl class=\"callToAction\"><dd><a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/en/about-us/location-zurich\" data-rit-tabid=\"135\">Zurich</a></dd></dl><dl class=\"callToAction\"><dd><a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/en/about-us/location-gossau-st-gallen\" data-rit-tabid=\"147\">Gossau St. Gallen</a></dd></dl><dl class=\"callToAction\"><dd><a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/en/about-us/location-lausanne\" data-rit-tabid=\"136\">Lausanne</a></dd></dl></div>\r\n<div><img id=\"Map\" src=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/Portals/0/Content/Location/map-ch.gif\" alt=\"Business Broker AG Map\" usemap=\"#map_ch\" border=\"0\" /><map name=\"map_ch\"></map></div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/en/about-us/location-zurich\" data-rit-tabid=\"135\">Zurich</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/en/about-us/location-gossau-st-gallen\" data-rit-tabid=\"147\">Gossau St. Gallen</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/en/about-us/location-lausanne\" data-rit-tabid=\"136\">Lausanne</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</article><article>\r\n<h2>Germany</h2>\r\n<div><dl class=\"callToAction\"><dd><a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/en/about-us/location-frankfurt-am-main\" data-rit-tabid=\"138\">Frankfurt am Main</a></dd></dl></div>\r\n<div><img id=\"Map\" src=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/Portals/0/Content/Location/map-de.gif\" alt=\"Business Broker AG Map\" usemap=\"#map_de\" border=\"0\" /><map name=\"map_de\"></map></div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/en/about-us/location-frankfurt-am-main\" data-rit-tabid=\"138\">Frankfurt am Main</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</article>','Locations','','inherit','closed','closed','','20-revision-v1','','','2015-12-18 14:56:23','2015-12-18 14:56:23','',20,'http://localhost/startupbroker/2015/12/18/20-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(111,1,'2015-12-18 14:57:12','2015-12-18 14:57:12','<h1>Testemonials</h1>\r\n<h2>This is what company owners say who have sold their business with the help of Business Broker AG</h2>\r\n<blockquote>I would like to thank you for the good times with you. It was fireworks through all the negotiations and discussions, thanks to you both I have come through everything so well.  The great result was awesome.\r\n\r\n<cite>Mrs. Graber, ex flower shop \"le clou\", Zurich</cite></blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>At first, I was sceptical as I believe that I am myself a good salesman and do not need help. I also found it expensive. Preparing company presentations by using the figures from the annual report was very interesting. After I had given you the mandate I found the total support and the quick sale very agreeable. Now, after the sale, I have to say that I have been very satisfied with your work. Thanks again.\r\n\r\n<cite>Mr. P. Gutenberg, ex Bakrona Zurich AG</cite></blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>Thank you very much for your help and your big effort. Of course I will recommend Business Broker AG whenever I can.  It is still difficult to say but I am looking forward to the next cooperation, you never know.\r\n\r\n<cite>Ercole Fusco, ex Fusco Plumbing GmbH</cite></blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>Working together with Business Broker AG was always a pleasure. The reception was very courteous, the execution of the work professional and quick. What I appreciated were the clear understandings which Mr. Schubert repeated after each meeting, so that everyone knew exactly what was meant. The strategies for the sale of my company were supported by a tightly led web portal, the presentation of which shows many years\' experience and is set up in a contemporary manner. Discretion was always a top priority; every interested party was bound to observe confidentiality. During the negotiations Mr. Schubert had the necessary calmness, which almost everyone in the position of selling their company is lacking. Also, a high level of know how is a very important factor which Business Broker AG have. I can therefore only recommend engaging the services of Business Broker AG when selling companies and for succession planning.\r\nI am convinced that success is not only achieved through ideas, strategies, goal settings and figures, it requires a human being who is also emotionally involved. Emotional decisions are the strength which is in us and which needs to be considered just as much as intelligence. From my point of view I have been able to experience this combination from Business Broker AG. It also touched me, that when I collected my documents after the sale, the team came together to congratulate me on my success. I felt happy after each visit; it also had something glorious about it because I was one step closer to my success. I would like to thank everyone for the exciting and wonderful time.\r\n\r\n<cite>Markus Anderegg, ex AM Caretaker</cite></blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>I wish you much success with selling. It is clear for me that you are the best and that I will recommend you anytime.\r\n\r\n<cite>Mrs. F. Fader, ex Move Fitness enter</cite></blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>What remains is to thank you for the steadfast commitment and for the excellent efforts to date.\r\n\r\n<cite>Mr. V. Niederberger, ex Londonhouse</cite></blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>No matter how it will develop, we have to thank you very much. We have been independent for almost two decades and we have experienced quite a lot. Your efficiency, paired with understanding and friendliness, is unique.\r\nContinue to work like this. We will make it up to you by referring as many as possible independent company owners wanting to sell to you. I hope that at least in this way we can stay in touch.\r\n\r\n<cite>Mr. Hoehler, Buyer Gallery Joy AG, Zurich</cite></blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>Firstly: Compliments for the home page, compliments for your efficient way of working, compliments for the excellent documentation.\r\n\r\n<cite>Mr. R.W., interested party, Fitness Centre Move, Zurich</cite></blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>Thank you very much for the prompt delivery of the documents regarding the company. How someone works says a lot about a person and his character. With all of you I have a good feeling to have\" landed\" at the right place.\r\n\r\n<cite>Mr. D.P. interested buyer, Event Agency</cite></blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>Dear Mr. Schaufelberger. I have seen the programme on Cash TV and after visiting your website I would like to congratulate you on this idea. As you know, first impressions count and remain. Should I have a company to sell, or would want to by one, I will come and see you. Best regards and much success!\r\n\r\n<cite>Mrs. M.V.Z.</cite></blockquote>\r\n<h2>This is what company owners have to say that have placed an advertisement with Business Broker AG</h2>\r\n<blockquote>I have had my company on your website for a while and I am well looked after und advised by your team.\r\n\r\n<cite>Mrs. M.H. owner fashion boutique</cite></blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>Hi, I have had my hairdressing salon advertised with Business Broker for about a month and I am totally enthusiastic. Over 20 interested parties have responded and soon I will decide for one of them. If I ever had to sell again, then only through Business Broker. Respect!\r\n\r\n<cite>Mr. L.T. owner hair dressing salon</cite></blockquote>','Testimonials','','inherit','closed','closed','','22-revision-v1','','','2015-12-18 14:57:12','2015-12-18 14:57:12','',22,'http://localhost/startupbroker/2015/12/18/22-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(112,1,'2015-12-18 14:57:57','2015-12-18 14:57:57','<h1>References</h1>\r\nThe following transactions have been concluded with the participation of members of our team giving advisory services in an operative or strategic way:\r\n\r\n<dl class=\"callToAction\"><dt>Impressions</dt> <dd><a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/Referenzen/Bildergalerie/tabid/140/Default.aspx\">Picture Gallery</a></dd></dl>\r\n<h2>Sale</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>E.S. TEAM-Service GmbH, turnover &lt; 1 Mio. CHF</li>\r\n	<li>Shardana Wellness- und Bodyforming Center, turnover &lt; 1 Mio. CHF</li>\r\n	<li>Schaffhauserplatz Apotheke, turnover &lt; 10 Mio. CHF</li>\r\n	<li>Hobli AG, turnover &lt; 1 Mio. CHF</li>\r\n	<li>Elektro Keller GmbH, turnover &lt; 5 Mio. CHF</li>\r\n	<li>Reitstahl Bikes, turnover &lt; 1 Mio. CHF</li>\r\n	<li>Galerie Joy AG, turnover &lt; 1 Mio. CHF</li>\r\n	<li>Blumen \"le clou\", turnover &lt; 1 Mio. CHF</li>\r\n	<li>S+M Technik, turnover &lt; 1 Mio. CHF</li>\r\n	<li>Sie &amp; Er Chemische Reinigung, turnover &lt; 1 Mio. CHF</li>\r\n	<li>A &amp; W Studios AG, turnover &lt; 1 Mio. CHF</li>\r\n	<li>Schlüssel Hug AG, turnover &lt; 10 Mio. CHF; <a href=\"http://www.busin